Wash and dry produce.

Trim and discard root end from @baby lettuce{1}; roughly chop. Halve, core, and
thinly slice @Granny Smith apple{1}. Cut @prosciutto{2%oz} into strips lengthwise, then
halve crosswise.

In a #large bowl{}, combine lettuce, apple, prosciutto, @dried cherries{1%oz},
@pepitas{1/2%oz}, and half the @Parmesan cheese{3%tbsp}.

Toss salad with as much @honey Dijon dressing{3%oz} as you like.

Divide salad between #bowls{}; garnish with remaining Parmesan. Serve.